name: Googlefaces
tagline: High quality JSF components for easy inclusion of Google Charts in JavaEE applications
body:
### Introduction.

GoogleFaces is a JSF library which provides a set of JSF components to use Google Charts in your JSF application.

## Example.
```xml
    <gf:pieChart title="TestChart" data="#{dataProvider.testData}" 
              var="data" value="#{data.value}" label="#{data.label}" />
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
